title: Welcome.to.the.Family.S01E01.HDTV.XviD-AFG
description:
Plot

The series follows the clash of cultures when Junior, the son of a Latino family, and Molly, the daughter of a Caucasian family, fall in love. After discovering that Molly is pregnant, the pair decide to get married, forcing a bonding and blending of their two very different families.

Cast

Mike O'Malley as Dr. Dan Yoder - father of Molly
Mary McCormack as Caroline Yoder
Ella Rae Peck as Molly Yoder
Joey Haro as Junior Hernandez
Ricardo Chavira as Miguel Hernandez 
Justina Machado as Lisette Hernandez
Fabrizio Zacharee Guido as Demetrio Hernandez
Eva Longoria as TBD
